{"tid":1080163,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣賽車風雲前傳　一句好廢觸發10萬元賭約","createTime":"2019-03-27T11:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:26:32.000Z","uid":172244,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"084a4f468e265b94e45be8e53771bcc8d47aaaaf","tid":1080163,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"2016年12月06日(二) 08:47<br />\n<br />\n荃灣昨晚有非法賽車活動，據悉勝出的車手可獲得10萬港元的賭注，不過原來背後亦涉及兩個車會之間的恩怨，網上流傳數段錄音，道出今次非法賽車的「前傳」。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據錄音內容，原來日前有司機駕駛其福士Scirocco ，載着一家大小於荃錦公路落山，尾隨一輛豐田AE111緊貼其後「推住行」，Scirocco司機不理該車，落到山與家人入餐廳食飯，期間豐田司機也進入餐廳，並說「Scirocco好廢」，並邀請他賽車，「路任你地揀咁話。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nScirocco司機因有家人在旁，故未有與他爭執，事後與所屬車會一名會員覆述事情，該名會員「好嬲」，覺得「依家唔係踩一個人，而係踩一班用Scirocco嘅人，而且玩車都唔使咁樣要走入餐廳攞彩。」遂「攞10萬出嚟賭佢地成個車會嘅牌簿（車輛登記文件）。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙方經聯絡後，約定「汀九停車場10點，帶定10萬蚊出嚟。」遂有今次的賽車活動發生，更有網民利用facebook live直播事件，從片段可見，現場有大批「花生友」圍觀，陸續有20多輛不同款式的辣車及客貨車入場，直播約12分鐘後，警車陸續到場控制場面，故雙方最終未有進行比賽，事件中有5輛私家車及2部客貨車疑涉非法改裝，被拖往大欖涌汽車扣留中心檢驗。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=2145846c&s={SIZE}\" />荃灣昨晚有非法賽車，多輛車涉非法改裝被警方扣驗。（讀者提供/冼耀華攝）<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_02p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=795b2d44&s={SIZE}\" />警方到場調查。（互聯網）<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_03p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=f87e4863&s={SIZE}\" />大批人士聚集。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_04p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=c9667f14&s={SIZE}\" />大批車輛到場。（讀者提供）<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_05p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=48431a33&s={SIZE}\" />涉案車輛被拖走檢驗。（互聯網）<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_06p.jpg?20161207061224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161206084752850-1206_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20161207061224&h=105db31b&s={SIZE}\" />車輛被拖往大欖涌汽車扣留中心。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3337738313a362fb9f16de1c269fc2bcb4d44148","tid":1080163,"uid":208241,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"ae111挑人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7afdce6949556cd019b8f16f843d88a9887b0d","tid":1080163,"uid":172244,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3337738313a362fb9f16de1c269fc2bcb4d44148","tid":1080163,"uid":208241,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"ae111挑人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"110 屌打"},{"pid":"303afecd5d75183c